data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features and open floor plan and TWO bonus rooms to be used as offices, bedrooms, playrooms, a formal dining, the list is endless. The kitchen overlooks the large living room with huge windows and high ceilings, the perfect space for entertaining. The living space continues outside on the custom built deck with perfectly maintained greenery, a canopy of trees, and accented with string lights for the most serene setting. Venture from the deck to the massive 20X30 shop with a bay door, AC, electricity, water, Luxury water softener and endless potential. Every room in this house is immaculately kept, spacious, and ready for you to call home! Call today to schedule your showing.
